\begin_inset Formula $F_{3}=-\frac{U_{i}}{2\pi\mathbf{i}}\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty}[G_{ii}^{<}(\omega)]_{41}\mathrm{d\omega}-\Delta_{i}$
\end_inset

, consider the derivative of 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{3}$
\end_inset

.
